_sText:
This is the fourth version of my jail map.

The features of this maps are:

- Minigame
- Climb
- Dodgeball
- Soccer
- Race
- Swimming Pool
- Healroom
- Camera Monitoring
- Disco [new]

Changes in this version:

- direct escape way from one cell is removed
- some textures got changed
- more decoration


Noblock is recommended for this map.

Please notify me if you have any suggestions or ideas for the next version.
